<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537158' id='t-537158'>that manifest themselves in our cities.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540980' id='t-540980'>The good news is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542506' id='t-542506'>and I do have good news to share with you,</span>
