<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548666' id='t-548666'>I have reason to believe</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550636' id='t-550636'>that it's possible for citizens to build</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553224' id='t-553224'>their own structures of participation.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='557757' id='t-557757'>Three years ago, I cofounded an organization</span>
