<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='569704' id='t-569704'>that they care about in their own city,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='572301' id='t-572301'>and have an impact on those causes and places</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='574990' id='t-574990'>every day.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='577318' id='t-577318'>In these past three years, Meu Rio grew</span>
