</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600828' id='t-600828'>Amongst our members is this adorable little girl,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='604460' id='t-604460'>Bia, to your right,</span>
